There are also special search functions users can choose:

*Browse Favorites
*Browse Recently Updated
*Browse Random Avatars
*Random From Current Search

Or simply, select the "Random Avatar" button to switch into a randomly selected avatar that's within the world's avatar database.

====Avatar favorites====
On the avatar pedestal of a searched avatar, users can click the star icon to favorite that avatar. These avatar favorites are only saved and viewable within the world, and users can save up to 500 avatars.

===Avatar roulette===
The Avatar Roulette feature is an opt-in gimmick which allows any user within the zone next to the mirror to "roulette" the avatar they're wearing. When a user clicks the "Avatar Roulette" button, every user's avatar within the zone will be randomly changed into an avatar that's within the world's avatar database.

===Portals===
Choosing the "Portals" tab on the settings panel will spawn many [[Special:MyLanguage/Portals|portals]] against the walls, in which users can go visit. These portals are separated by category:

*My Worlds: Worlds made by Prismic247; the author of the world.
*Avatar Worlds
*Game Worlds
*Variety Worlds

Users can also load any world on a portal via world ID.

